				<properties name="WMDR2-core" type="Logical" documentation="wmdr2-core v0.2.x&#xA;v0.2.5&#xA;- break association between Deployment and ObservationSeries in favor of an association Deployment-ObservingConfiguration. This ObservingConfiguration is the new class name for ObservingMethod.&#xA;- rename association roles to conventional UML naming.&#xA;v0.2.5.1&#xA;- drop observingConfiguration.date as being redundant to Deployment.date for almost all use cases identified.&#xA;v0.2.5.2&#xA;- Deployment.exposure moved to ObservingConfiguration.exposure&#xA;- Deployment.operatingStatus moved to ObservingConfiguration.operatingStatus&#xA;- Deployment.date moved to ObservingConfiguration.date to facilitate reconstruction of ObservationSeries history"/>
